      <div class="repair-card">
        <h3>Smeg FAB28URRD1 retro refrigerator, Venice</h3>
        <p><strong>Symptom:</strong> Owner noticed the gasket on the lower edge of the door was no longer sealing — visible gap, condensation forming on the door frame, fridge cycling more than usual. Unit was 7 years old in a Venice canal-area design renovation, cream color.</p>
